{"tid":746033,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"狗會同練狗師方加柏害撚死人","createTime":"2018-07-17T09:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T02:59:48.000Z","uid":29086,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a7469e8bca789a2dcc45099f821cbfd1e6cdc22","tid":746033,"uid":29086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"【嚴重意外】前見習騎師莫振華 頭部受創一度昏迷搶救！<br />\n<br />\n行船跑馬三分險！眾所周知騎師係高危行業，騎喺馬背上風險不小，日常負責替馬匹操練嘅騎馬人，亦周不時都會受傷發生意外。今早（17日）沙田馬場亦發生一宗騎馬人墮馬受傷事件。<br />\n<br />\n雖然馬季剛歇暑，跑道封閉，但馬匹仍會保持運動量，亦會拉出馬房範圍內騎踱，今晨約6時左右，方嘉柏馬房的騎馬人（俗稱助手）莫振華策騎馬匹在馬房地堂踱步，不慎被馬匹拋下，遭馬匹壓着及被踢中頭部腦出血，據知傷勢頗嚴重，一度陷入昏迷，須立即送到沙田威爾斯醫院搶救，莫振華曾經醒過，但目前仍在深切治療部，情況危殆。<br />\n現年39歲的莫振華是1996至1997年度第16屆見習騎師，父親莫錦倫亦是資深馬房工作人員，他跟隨前練馬偉王登平學藝，策騎成績一般，不久退居幕後。同屆見習騎師簡慧榆及鄭昌達，已先後在1999年及2000年因陣上墮馬意外身故。至於另一位同屆見習生余健雄，現時則在澳門策騎。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20180717/58452222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F58452222&d=dY1SNdcIbrVQgb7bjg36EQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5e806ea4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F58452222&h=d5594bd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20180717/58452222</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新報馬經 HKDN Racing<br />\n1 hr &middot; <br />\n【嚴重意外】今晨方廐騎馬人莫振華在馬房內操馬時不慎墮馬，先被馬匹壓倒，跟手再被馬腳踢中頭部，傷勢非常嚴重，救護員即時將他送院救治，疑因腦部出血昏迷，情況甚嚴重，現時他在威爾斯醫院深切治療部正在搶救中，希望他可吉人天相<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">抖暑期間無白車STAND BY, 係唔比騎馬, 死仆街印度仔驚撚死蝕底, 照操, 搞到受左傷無得即時送院, 要等白車, 遲左救, 而家生死未卜, 人地2個仔先得2歲同5歲,陰公</span></span>"},{"pid":"1794ddb32ee237063ca06bb86630b7296ad3fcff","tid":746033,"uid":3363,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><code>因「洗版行為」，帳號已被封鎖直至 2048-07-17 00:46:08</code></blockquote>"},{"pid":"987d287a5649aa7efb2a4d14131edb40711df452","tid":746033,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"莫振華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港好多過氣見習生/華將一直仲係hkjc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bf17aebfe5f23d7613982768afb26f26d6b498","tid":746033,"uid":29086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"987d287a5649aa7efb2a4d14131edb40711df452","tid":746033,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"莫振華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港好多過氣見習生/華將一直仲係hkjc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"余健誠, 何志文, 鍾麗芳, 蘇錦文,黃志雄,曾超祺,李啟榮"},{"pid":"081021c8d07d31a4fc32496bb6be1e0de59497e9","tid":746033,"uid":29086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:13:49.000Z","msg":"前見習騎師莫振華 沙田馬場墮馬危殆<br />\n<br />\n34,736<br />\n最後更新: 0717 15:00 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0717 07:32<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【15:00】莫振華目前情況仍然危殆<br />\n<br />\n沙田馬場發生墮馬意外，清晨約6時，39歲騎馬人莫振華在馬場訓練馬匹時意外墮馬，被馬匹壓倒昏迷，職員報警。救護員趕到送院搶救，疑腦部大量出血，情況危殆。<br />\n莫振華於96至97年度曾任見習騎師，跟隨前練馬偉王登平。<br />\n馬會指一位策騎員今晨於沙田馬場晨操期間受傷， 隨即被送往醫院救治，並已即時聯絡其家人，會盡力作出協助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新消息: 要叫齊家人朋友去醫院     印度仔就風流快活緊</span></span>"},{"pid":"8813fd00da83550d85d480bad9d82311711df4a1","tid":746033,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"即係咁多間公眾騎術學校長期有白車standby?"},{"pid":"3cee105e1e72f4846ffb8427b7352fbac9d7b3c1","tid":746033,"uid":29086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8813fd00da83550d85d480bad9d82311711df4a1","tid":746033,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"即係咁多間公眾騎術學校長期有白車standby?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該無,  不過沙田馬場係要有白車STAND BY先操得馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83675e1d3c6ad54ce1a8f76443280ce7e7b02192","tid":746033,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28bf17aebfe5f23d7613982768afb26f26d6b498","tid":746033,"uid":29086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"987d287a5649aa7efb2a4d14131edb40711df452","tid":746033,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"莫振華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港好多過氣見習生/華將一直仲係hkjc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"余健誠, 何志文, 鍾麗芳, 蘇錦文,黃志雄,曾超祺,李啟榮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"當年解釋斷咗腳踏選擇跳馬既羅德權都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知退休未呢"},{"pid":"cf1f5938a8dbf0c635270b0d479e9efc1f575f50","tid":746033,"uid":29086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83675e1d3c6ad54ce1a8f76443280ce7e7b02192","tid":746033,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28bf17aebfe5f23d7613982768afb26f26d6b498","tid":746033,"uid":29086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"987d287a5649aa7efb2a4d14131edb40711df452","tid":746033,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"莫振華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港好多過氣見習生/華將一直仲係hkjc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"余健誠, 何志文, 鍾麗芳, 蘇錦文,黃志雄,曾超祺,李啟榮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"當年解釋斷咗腳踏選擇跳馬既羅德權都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n